// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3674 — Mass File Rename (ransomed)
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: db3fee1a-41c7-5679-8942-4190fa830ec2

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
